Remarks.
There is no marked difference between the dorsal setal measurements of our specimen and the original one (
Table 8
). The length of the ventrianal shield in our specimen (
92 µm
) is slightly longer than the earlier one (
73 µm
), apart from this other measurements agree with the available measurements of the former species.
